column811: We own a Massey Ferguson HD 2660 and the Tach does not work. It does not show engine speed, engine hours or the speed of the PTO. I have asked several dealers and know dealer has ever had that problem. I was told just buy a new Tach. and that will take care of it. Well I do I know buying a new $500.00 Tach will take care of the problem. No dealer has ever offered to check my problem or tell me what I need to check. We have owned Massey Ferguson tractors since they were painted gray and were called Ferguson. The oldest tractor we did own was a 1956 Ferguson. Since then we bought a new 135 Deluxe Multipower diesel and we bought a MF¬†175 with the multipower. This problem if not repaired is going to cause us to buy another brand of tractor very shortly. We had one problem with it when it was brand new. The hydraulic filter was stopped up with metal cuttings. We were shocked when we drained the transmission oil and the drain plug had chunks of metal stuck to it. We had to change the hygralic oil twice( you know that isn't cheap) and the oil filters twice. That is the 1st. time we had ever seen that out of a new tractor. The company didn't pay for the oil or the filters. So the Tach that doesn't work is the final straw......I think the company should pay for the oil and filters and repair the Tach. Enough is enough.....If the tach isn't repaired free that will be the last Massey we own. We even own a Massey Ferguson 2400 lawn tractor with a front end loader mounted on it. By the way the Tach. quit working on it and the cruise control never did work. I hope your MF equipment works without all the problems we have......Larry Bleigh¬† Phone 3o4 742 3129..............‚Ä®269

column11884: Dear Mahindra‚Ä®            Because of  this exciting feature ( Position Auto control) of JIVO 365 tractor,‚Ä®I brought this machine in March 2019. Mahindra claims ‚Äúwith PAC, the Rotavator can automatically adjust the puddling depth, without any need for adjustment to PC  lever‚Äù. For a tractor driver/ farmer this feature matters more. Later I realized this feature is bogus. After repeated complaints technical staff from direct Mahindra came for inspection after 3 months from delivery .  But they were not able to rectify the same. Still the complaint stays  unrectified. Another thing , parts are not available for this machine. For the last one month the machine is with dealer work shop . For every part we have to wait  for it to reach from the plant -dealer says.  For every repair/ service I need to stall the machine for min 30 days.  How can I move ahead with this machine. Request Mahindra either to  refund me or to demonstrate the automated working of  rotavator.  Transmission oil leakage,  engine over heating, front differential oil leakage are  extra benefits for me .  Dear Mahindra ..for you it is first time  revolutionary technology in our country and revenue, but for me loss of money and  feels like getting cheated .Financier for this machine is Mahindra Finance. So you earn  two revenue. As a farmer I request / wish to get my money back , and I believe i will,  because I am sharing my grievance to an industrialist not to a business man.     ‚Ä®                                                                 Posted on 18.09.2020. Mahindra claims ‚Äúwith PAC, the Rotavator can automatically adjust the puddling depth, without any need for adjustment to PC  lever‚Äù. For a tractor driver/ farmer this feature matters more. Later I realized this feature is bogus. After repeated complaints technical staff from direct Mahindra came for inspection after 3 months from delivery .  But they were not able to rectify the same. Still the complaint stays  unrectified. Another thing , parts are not available for this machine. For the last one month the machine is with dealer work shop . For every part we have to wait  for it to reach from the plant -dealer says.  For every repair/ service I need to stall the machine for min 30 days.  How can I move ahead with this machine. Request Mahindra either to  refund me or to demonstrate the automated working of  rotavator.  Transmission oil leakage,  engine over heating, front differential oil leakage are  extra benefits for me .  Dear Mahindra ..for you it is first time  revolutionary technology in our country and revenue, but for me loss of money and  feels like getting cheated .Financier for this machine is Mahindra Finance. So you earn  two revenue. As a farmer I request / wish to get my money back , and I believe i will,  because I am sharing my grievance to an industrialist not to a business man.     ‚Ä®                                                                 Posted on 18.09.2020.
